TEXT.S: = Maylubung = Gaga mniq Myawriseyn Tayansyang ka alang Maylubung. 66 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 191 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 93% niqan 178 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 7% niqan 13 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 91%, Amis 1%, Bunun 1%, Cou 1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%.
